        "subject": "LU-3556 osd-ldiskfs: simple code cleanup",
        "message": "LU-3556 osd-ldiskfs: simple code cleanup\n\nThe second part of the patch with a simple code cleanup:\n - rename BYPASS_CAPA to LC_BYPASS_CAPA to make it less generic\n   for upstream submission\n - rename md[dt]_set_capainfo() to md[dt]_capainfo_set(), the same\n   for mdt_dump_capainfo()\n\nSigned-off-by: Dmitry Eremin <dmitry.eremin@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I328e4efc041c61f12f56079af0541678fe7d7cfb\n"
